fr.sorbonne_u.components.hem2024e1.utils

Interface MeasureI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, TimingI
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompoundMeasure, Measure

    public interface MeasureI
extends TimingI, java.io.Serializable
    The class MeasureI mainly marks classes from which instance of measures are represented; the two major subclasses currently proposed represent scalar and compound measures (made of scalar measures), hence the presence of the method isScalar().

    Description

    White-box Invariant
